source.comments:
Create the query and variables field for the GraphQL payload. 

The priority is the current time - update date (with text) of the record. This is rough, since the updated date is a date, so the timestamp is set to midnight, so priority goes down as the day progresses, but dates still work.
source.name: Create graphql params
